Preconditions:
- The input strings `text` and `pattern` are not null.
- The length of `text` is at least 1 and at most 10^5.
- The length of `pattern` is exactly 2.
- `text` and `pattern` consist only of lowercase English letters.

Postconditions:
- The method returns a long value representing the maximum number of times `pattern` can occur as a subsequence of the modified `text`.